Task: Create ProgressCard component

Summary: Implemented ProgressCard component for displaying module/unit progress with visual progress bar and next lesson CTA.

Changes:
- Created components/student/ProgressCard.tsx with:
  - Progress display with percentage
  - Visual progress bar with smooth transitions
  - Color coding: orange for in-progress, green for completed
  - Next lesson information with 'Start Lesson' CTA button
  - Completed state with checkmark icon and 'Completed!' message
  - Proper ARIA attributes for accessibility (progressbar role)
- Updated components/student/index.ts to export ProgressCard
- Created comprehensive test suite (__tests__/components/student/ProgressCard.test.tsx) with 13 tests covering:
  - Title and percentage rendering
  - Next lesson CTA rendering
  - Progress bar width and behavior (0%, 100%, intermediate values)
  - Completion state handling
  - Accessibility (ARIA roles and labels)

Why: Progress visualization is essential for students to track their learning journey. The card provides clear feedback on completion status and encourages continued learning with prominent CTAs.

